HEADWORD: Rouncy
<hw>Roun"cy</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A common hackney
horse; a nag.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>he rode upon a <qex>rouncy</qex> as he could.</q>
<rj><qau>Chaucer.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Round</ent>⟦br⟧
